MotionControlData.programScript:
#setup
'GENERAL SETTINGS
BR -1
ER 10000
OE 0
MT 1
CE 2
CN 1
BWA=100
SB2
SB3
II2,,,2

'Default Profile Parameters
dx=29999
speed=1000
delay=1000
maxdepth=300000
rtdist = 1000
rtfq = 20
rtpause = 1000
step = 1.0
cutdone=0
secdone=0
initgap=1000
touchst = 0
ppos = 0
homest=0

'Default PID PARAMETERS
kdtoff = 60.0
kptoff = 30.0
kitoff = 2.0
kddef = 35.0
kpdef = 3.0
kidef = 1.0

KD kddef
KP kpdef
KI kidef


'Default SPEEDS & ACCELERATIONS
SP 50000
AC 1000000
DC 1000000
EN

'Default Offsets
OF -3.2
IL 10
FV 0
FA 0

#latch
'SET SPEEDS & ACCELERATIONS
SP 50000
AC 1000000
DC 1000000
PR 20000;BG
AM;ST
JP #home
EN

'**************************************
'EMERGENCY STOP
'**************************************
#ININT
MG "Interrupt"
ST
SB2
WT500
MO
MG "Emergency Stop Detected"
#WAIT
JP#WAIT,@IN[2]=1
JS#RESETI
ZS
MG "Emergency Stop Cleared"
EN
#RESETI
RI2

'**************************************
'Linear Move
'**************************************
'Will move at a constant rate

#linemv
startpos = _TPA
ppos = _TPA
finalmv = startpos+maxdepth

cutdone=0;
KD kdtoff
KP kptoff
KI kitoff
MG "Linear Move Start"
SP speed
CB2
PR maxdepth;BG
#reportp
ppos=_TPA
JP #reportp, ppos<finalmv
AM
KD kddef
KP kpdef
KI kidef
SB2;ST
MG "Profile Complete"

'return to profile start location
SP 50000
x=-1*maxdepth
PR x;BG;
AM;ST;
cutdone=1
EN

'**************************************
'Vibration Profile
'**************************************
'Will retract at set intervals

#vibmv

cutdone=0;

MG "Vibration Profile Start"


startpos = _TPA
nextpos = _TPA
ppos = _TPA
SP 1000000
backsp = 50000000
forsp = 50000000
KD 50
KP 14
KI 2
FA 0
FV 0
IL 10
rtpause = 8

finalmv = startpos+maxdepth

XQ #vmove, 1

#fndepth
curpos=_TPA
JP #fndepth, curpos<finalmv
MG "Reached max depth"
ST; HX1; SB2
cutdone = 1
HX
EN

#polish
secdone = 0
step = 0
fntime = 25000

XQ #vmove, 1

WT fntime
ST; HX1; SB2
WT 1000

MG "Profile Complete"

'return to profile start location
SP 50000
KD kddef
KP kpdef
KI kidef
FV 0
FA 0
IL 10
WT 1000
secdone = 1
HX
EN
 

#vmove
PA nextpos;BG;AM
WT5
ppos = _TPA
CB2
WT rtfq
SB2
nextpos = nextpos+step
AC backsp
DC backsp
PR -rtdist;BG;AM
WT rtpause
AC backsp
DC forsp
PR rtdist;BG;AM
JP #vmove
EN

'**************************************
'SUBROUTINES
'**************************************

#home
homest = 0
JG-5000, (_LR=0);
BG;AM;ST;
DP*=0
WT 1000
homest = 1
EN
'**************************************

'**************************************
#touchof
'**************************************
elimit= 40
Merr = 50
touchst = 0
ztouch = 0
n=0

KD kdtoff
KP kptoff
KI kitoff
'
IF touchref>0
SP 100000
WT 500
PA touchref;BG;AM
WT 500
ENDIF

JP#STERR, @IN[1]=0
XQ #TOUCHS, 1
XQ #errChk, 2
'
EN
'
#TOUCHS
JG500;BG
#CHECK1
JP #CHECK1, @IN[1]=1
ST
WT500
zpos0 = _TPA

SP 20000
PR-600; BG; AM; ST
JG500;BG
#CHECK2
JP #CHECK2, @IN[1]=1
ST
WT500
zpos1 = _TPA

SP 20000
PR-600; BG; AM; ST
JG500;BG
#CHECK3
JP #CHECK3, @IN[1]=1
ST
WT500
zpos2 = _TPA

JP #INCON, (zpos0-zpos1)>Merr
JP #INCON, (zpos0-zpos2)>Merr
JP #INCON, (zpos1-zpos2)>Merr
JP #INCON, (zpos1-zpos0)>Merr
JP #INCON, (zpos2-zpos0)>Merr
JP #INCON, (zpos2-zpos1)>Merr
ztouch = (zpos0+zpos1+zpos2)/3

SP500;PA ztouch; BG; AM; ST

MG "Zero point found"
SP 100000
PR-initgap; BG
AM
touchst = 1
MG "Complete"
KD kddef
KP kpdef
KI kidef
HX
EN
'
#errChk
error=_TEA;
JP #errChk, error<elimit
ST
'
#Error
MG "Positional error limit exceeded"
touchst = 2
KD kddef
KP kpdef
KI kidef
HX
EN
'
#INCON
MG "Inconsitent Touch Position"
touchst = 2
KD kddef
KP kpdef
KI kidef
HX
EN
'
#STERR
MG "Already touching part"
touchst = 3
KD kddef
KP kpdef
KI kidef
EN
'

#BINARYF 
time=150
CB3
WTtime
SB3
WTtime
JP#BINARYF
EN
